00:20:55,790 --> 00:20:59,100
it has, like, a thousand
different applications, so...

489
00:20:59,140 --> 00:21:01,010
sorry.
I blew it.

490
00:21:01,060 --> 00:21:02,710
Seems to be my thing today.

491
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:04,670
- Hey,

492
00:21:04,710 --> 00:21:06,110
what's going on, Chester?

493
00:21:06,150 --> 00:21:07,800
I'm sensing
a whole lot of sadness.

494
00:21:07,850 --> 00:21:09,500
- Yeah, aren't you supposed
to still be with Ray?

495
00:21:09,550 --> 00:21:13,070
- I have resigned
as Ray's liaison.

496
00:21:13,110 --> 00:21:15,120
It turns out
I messed that up, too.

497
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:17,030
Now I'm, like, dead to him.

498
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:23,300
Oh, my God, Cecil,
I am--I'm so sorry.

499
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:24,730
I shouldn't have said that.
