00:21:36,050 --> 00:21:37,790
at the craps table
with Grandma Runk.

506
00:21:37,830 --> 00:21:40,010
I mean, Tech Con's paying
in cryptocurrency this year,

507
00:21:40,050 --> 00:21:41,360
which barely feels like
real money,

508
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,450
even though it totally is.

